Sentencas: The subsolidus phase relations in the La-Fe-Al-O system were investigated for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) applications.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase relations in the La2O3-Fe2O3-Al2O3 system

Sentencas: Five compounds, LaAlO(3), LaAl(11)O(18), LaFe(12)O(19), AlFeO(3), and LaFeO(3), coexist in the La-Fe-Al-O system at 1380 degreesC in air.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase relations in the La2O3-Fe2O3-Al2O3 system

Sentencas: The microstructure and composition of the samples were studied by x-ray diffractometry and scanning electron microscopy.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase relations in the La2O3-Fe2O3-Al2O3 system

Sentencas: Based on experimental evidence, a phase diagram of the La(2)O(3)-Al(2)O-Fe(2)O(3) system has been proposed.
